'''''Bull Fight''''' is a coin-operated [[arcade game]] produced by [[Sega]] in 1984.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Killer List of Videogames]]|title=Bull Fight|url=https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7231}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bull Fight|publisher=[[MobyGames]]|url=https://www.mobygames.com/game/bullfight}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bull Fight|website=flyers.arcade-museum.com|url=https://flyers.arcade-museum.com/?page=thumbs&db=videodb&id=2519}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bull Fight|website=segaretro.org|date=26 August 2019 |url=https://segaretro.org/Bullfight}}</ref>

==Description==
The player assumes the role of a [[bullfighter]] attempting to defeat a [[bull]]. The bullfighter is controlled via a [[joystick]] and two buttons.

